There’s more to this amazingly tiny tome than meets the eye… besides being remarkably #charming, it’s also vanishingly rare… because this is the first miniature book produced by the sixteenth century #printing pioneer, Christophe Plantin. Prosperous and prolific, Plantin’s Press at #Antwerp was a powerhouse of fine printing that created some of the most complex productions of the period. This ‘Kalendarium. Evangelia 4. Psalmi poenit. 7’ (‘Calendar. The Four Gospels. Psalms 7’), has been printed in red and black #gothic type and dates from 1570. It also retains its contemporary #binding of gilt covers, clasps and gauffered (patterned) edges - (Lot 103 in Auction 24115 - Fine Books and Manuscripts - 14th June – Estimate: £5,000 - £7,000) - #Bonhams #Books #Book #Libro #Livre #Buch #本 #书 #도서 #boek #Bok #kirja #Bookstagram #BookstagramFeature #Instabook #RareBooks #MiniatureBook #Miniature #AntiquarianBooks

So, last night I got my @flavnt_streetwear #bareskin binder. No other binder has made me this flat, ESPECIALLY when wearing only one. For those of you that don't know, a binder is an undergarment for transmasculine people who want to have a flatter appearing chest. For someone like me who has a DD chest, no binder seems to work - it gives the appearance of a uniboob, doesn't get you very flat and/or is incredibly uncomfortable. I've tried every mainstream/well known binder out there. I've been waiting and waiting for something better. I can say without an ounce of hesitation that I've found it. My chest has never been more flat. I've never felt more comfortable. And for the first time since I started wearing binders, I can wear just one out of the house and feel comfortable. I've been in love with #FLAVNT since the first day I found out about them and this makes me love them that much more. I'll do a blog post to cover everything this binder does for me, but here's your sneak peek. Stay tuned. I may or may not have cried when I put this on. Thank you, @seethestarsablaze & @courtney__25 for being amazing human beings who also put everyone else above themselves. #flavntyourself #flavntstreetwear #lgbt #lgbtq #queer #trans #transgender #transmasculine #transguy #binder #binding #confidence #bodyupdate #15monthsont #hrt #testosterone
